Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:52.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\fs50\pos(1055,1010)}Necro
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:55.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}苦しみだけ置いていくはず
